author: David Aaro
title: US spies having trouble assessing coronavirus spread in China, Russia: report
description: With nearly 800,000 coronavirus cases worldwide, Intelligence agencies in the U.S. are having difficulties determining the situation in areas such as China, Russia, and North Korea, government sources told Reuters.
